test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -16 == -32
 +  where -16 = <built-in function prod>([-16])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x748cca262940>([-32])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x748cca262940> = [[1], [1, -32], [-32, 1], [-32, 1, -32], [1], [1, -32], ...].count
